					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">In general you might want also to consider things that can be included with the cart purchase as an added incentive to get the real thing.  I have no idea what your game is, but I think simple things that personalize the object make it much more valuable to the customer.  Part of what you're selling is participation in the scene so play to it and add in something cool like a booklet documenting your design process or a printout of parts of your source code.  The other thing you're selling is the object itself, so you might consider doing a a limited run of your carts and numbering them, or add in an instruction manual + map, something to make it more of an <strong>object</strong>.</div>

